messages.tl: How, how come! ! I don't want to die...!

messages.zh: 用法术击毁建筑做掩体！！
messages.tl: Uses to destroy the building as a bunker! !

messages.zh: 这里不是天灾中心区！能行！！
messages.tl: This is not the center of the natural disaster! Can do it! !

messages.zh: 有陨石撞击了临街建筑！卧倒！！
messages.tl: There are meteorites hitting the street building! Lying down! !

messages.zh: 要求罗德岛术师射击坠石
messages.tl: Ask Rhodes Island Master to shoot the Falling Stone
Explode it, blow it up, ah ah--! !

messages.zh: 交叉火力成功击碎了岩体？！
messages.tl: Cross firepower successfully crushed the rock mass? !

messages.zh: 下次我可不一定能救到你！！
messages.tl: I won't be able to save you next time! !
The Reunion Movement suffered heavy casualties -!

messages.zh: 如果不击碎落石的话，我们也要被波及——！
messages.tl: If we don't break the rock, we will be affected too!

messages.zh: 啊啊啊！！罗德岛！！别想走！！去死！！！
messages.tl: Ah! ! Rhodes Island! ! Don't think about leaving! ! Go to hell! ! !

messages.zh: ——整合运动向我们发动进攻了？
messages.tl: - The Reunion Movement launched an attack on us?

messages.zh: 这些混蛋，是被天灾逼疯了吗？！！
messages.tl: Are these bastards driven by natural disasters? ! !

messages.zh: 命令临光带队向下城区出口移动
messages.tl: Order Nearl to take the team to the city exit
